    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger door, and some clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but the driver's seat shows significant wear and the infotainment screen has a few dead pixels. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but you may notice a slight vibration at highway speeds and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid option for someone looking for transportation at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
