    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been absolute gold. It's in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-loved! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a fantastic vehicle that\u2019s got plenty of life left. Come take a look, I'm sure you're going to love it!",
