    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration. Recent valve lash adjustments and consistent fluid analysis confirm the internal health of the S54. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain and throttle response remain sharp, delivering the quintessential analog M-car experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
