    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though closer inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only slight curbing on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of rips or tears, and the bolsters remain firm. All electronic components\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, infotainment system, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection completed last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two sets of keys, and a thick folder of service records. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
