    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. If you're looking for a reliable, great-looking car that still has tons of life left in it, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
