    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox, the drivetrain remains robust with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system and shimmed valve clearances. The chassis benefits from reinforced rear subframe mounting points and polyurethane bushings, ensuring the variable M differential lock translates torque to the tarmac with surgical precision. While the bodywork shows honest patina consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are sorted, including a refreshed cooling system and upgraded rod bearings. A turn-key performance icon for the purist who values mechanical integrity over a garage-queen status.",
